  "title": "Software Engineer (SaMD) Healthcare",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our Client is one of the leading player in healthcare industry. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Software Engineer (SaMD) to be part of their IT team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the Central Area - easily accessible.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities of Software Engineer (SaMD):</strong></p><ul><li>Implement risk management best practices for innovation projects and support adoption/commercialization.</li><li>Maintain ISO 13485 & IEC 62304-compliant quality management processes across projects.</li><li>Provide guidance on regulatory, quality, and risk requirements for Software-as-Medical-Device (SaMD) projects.</li><li>Perform clinical need validation, risk assessments, and de-risking of proposed solutions.</li><li>Support project management, grant recommendations, milestone tracking, and KPI achievement.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Degree in IT, Computer Science or related field</li><li>5 - 8 years of experience in full software development life cycles.</li><li>Familiar with framework such as GCP, AWS, SQL and Azure is required.</li><li>Exposure to ISO and Quality/Risk Management aspects in healthcare or medical context is a bonus.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><strong>Email Address: Jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><ul><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</li></ul>",
